,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:42:45.000Z","msg":"係中環成條街掛哂美國旗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗起個場面都興奮"},{"pid":"1c1693f8dea8c4284ca3e3c350703fa210656a7a","tid":2041033,"uid":25147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:10:27.000Z","msg":"認同街頭抗爭個part 成本效益比一年低左太多 因為對家已經無哂所有底線"},{"pid":"8df3d2d62ca87098d73224b1b4b9e799defb6134","tid":2041033,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ecfd03b67b3a7b74670ed4668d9f8b6d051bd5","tid":2041033,"uid":29532,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"同意樓主嗰句 只要香港人一息尚存 就會仲有抗爭<br />\n所以應該要以延續香港民族意識為主要目的 <br />\n喺而家香港街頭衝突成效不如以往既情況下 就算你激到習近平中風都只會令我地死快啲<br />\n我認為喺呢段時間<br />\n讀多啲書 操fit自己 提高香港國民質素<br />\n為日後建國作準備 就係目前除咗抗爭外最需要做既事"},{"pid":"61b80500f54c05366935b8b186d4bcf73f54b5c5","tid":2041033,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a4f7ca7583fa328411cb256ba1587f6723b6717","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"和你批 批鬥元氣 托鬥吉野家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:14:34.000Z","msg":"係中國人就唔好幫襯小日本嘅壽司店同牛肉飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b71c8da4039b57bc3ed22acd6c21535a88090d","tid":2041033,"uid":134323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"幫澳洲賣牛肉農產品"},{"pid":"bf051585cdefff37e92b57d905fd4d021afe0981","tid":2041033,"uid":92433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2113492c5c9db62469b2f0f1d3cbcb22eedf9f","tid":2041033,"uid":94291,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b6e4a6b16e4f8f2dd97b66f5fc8c7b6b5ad6b935","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"我相信冇人會忘記2019年 只要香港人一息尚存 就會仲有抗爭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NY936Ad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNY936Ad.gif&h=f8fcc08a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"我都想拍段咁既野po ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc184831c5fb8ac850992fdb75f58da445d41679","tid":2041033,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:21:51.000Z","msg":"全球黃色經濟圈"},{"pid":"35472bedf9d79859cb56635a78b0d87b1c360e8a","tid":2041033,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:23:41.000Z","msg":"Yes I agree"},{"pid":"c589ac410b438fd625ff914e16efb0f0365ecfc8","tid":2041033,"uid":306621,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c34983377e742761f90739d7f890c81e46b60f4d","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"like":90,"dislike":3,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"閱讀前提<br />\n1, 香港人可以將抗爭融入生活 e.g.黃色經濟圈。<br />\n2, 香港獨立逐漸成為主流，留戀街頭抗爭意義及目的不大。<br />\n3, 狗隻已完全掌握過去1年嘅所有抗爭模式 e.g. 5.27港九新界佈陣。<br />\n4, 勇武抗爭到達樽頸位，面對水炮車、震撼彈等理大戰時所用武器已經無計可施，同時難以在本地升級 e.g. 炸藥、槍、軍隊。<br />\n5, 裝修對經濟打擊喺旅遊業復甦前不大，影響亦遠不及一次武漢肺炎。<br />\n6, 唔駛諗咩大罷工同全民勇武。講咗成年喇，死心啦。手足擋子彈擋到變蜂巢都唔會罷工。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:24:18.000Z","msg":"即係叫人咩都唔好做, 食黃店, 幻想自己抗爭咗, 然後再過一代人,<br />\n香港人變成小粉紅, <br />\n<br />\n我既理解有冇錯?"},{"pid":"0922f1131cf1ec42f0b917b7fea5c81c48200812","tid":2041033,"uid":112467,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"改兩隻字唱完即刻變禁歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起來！不願做奴隸的人們！<br />\n把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span></strong></span>民族到了最危險的時候<br />\n每個人被迫著發出最後的吼聲。<br />\n起來！起來！起來！<br />\n我們萬眾一心<br />\n冒著敵人的炮火前進！<br />\n冒著敵人的炮火前進！<br />\n前進！前進！進！"},{"pid":"4309522e254b70dc9420355edc18ca38bf13fb10","tid":2041033,"uid":92859,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nexAXYb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnexAXYb.jpg&h=d258a04e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjDsO42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjDsO42.jpg&h=d0946da8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbb3734efab66616837ebcbec26e5f7b4be8f941","tid":2041033,"uid":44654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e572314852a68b8168249184f3da1d4eb645b34c","tid":2041033,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51a26eda1afb1c30fa38edde3679b99930fe156","tid":2041033,"uid":236538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/2cdbf5de-10c7-11ea-bbc7-005056a99247/w:900/p:16x9/capturexietsesamantes.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F2cdbf5de-10c7-11ea-bbc7-005056a99247%2Fw%3A900%2Fp%3A16x9%2Fcapturexietsesamantes.png&h=072bedbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"665146bfe617c36ea94fea5972cef563ffb81340","tid":2041033,"uid":127783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"批鬥外國護照 批鬥移民 邊個移民邊個就是漢奸<br />\n爭取美英澳加唔俾支那人留學移民<br />\n一齊留喺中國攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ae580352d98e32528a907a3ea88e36ebe3f0cc","tid":2041033,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ee5c4c124e9fba51e3e2a2bf5c5b5e6e61d1111","tid":2041033,"uid":53922,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:42:45.000Z","msg":"係中環成條街掛哂美國旗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10441eee6f72109602de642f85424a254cd4360","tid":2041033,"uid":309079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"地厚天高句quote<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ee91864808486624b6f622c371bc5543f170bb","tid":2041033,"uid":264887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:05:11.000Z","msg":"push，上年六月我地創意爆棚，係時候出番個勢黎"},{"pid":"91ed464624886434805fbd35b55f047b7cc3e5e6","tid":2041033,"uid":288463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09d8c841337688ea162412468ddf962340ee9ca5","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TL;DR 創意抗爭更能吸引外媒目光，使參與抗爭門檻更低，幽默情節在社會中更能成為話題。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n國安法將臨，雖然國際間好消息不絕，但離中共倒台仍確實有一段距離。經過1年的精神繃緊，不少和理非及淺黃已拒絕接收抗爭消息或出席任何集會遊行。5.27等目標不明確的集會、黃店/kol互咬、捉鬼隊、送頭論等亦使眾手足不斷內鬥、互罵、消耗抗爭能量，使情勢不容樂觀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，希望大家要面對現實，我地依家追求嘅唔再係五大訴求咁簡單，係民族自治、係脫離中共管治、係港獨、係推翻中共政權。 At least, 對家係咁諗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6CUqOG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6CUqOG.jpg&h=12bf7bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地眼前嘅敵人已經不再是擅長分化淺黃、可以遊花園遊到去對面海等較高章政治手段嘅港共政權，或者周身屎嘅販冰兵，而係不惜搲爛塊面都要作戰狼外交、有前冇後嘅中共團隊。縱然其資源及權力都較港共多及大，但手段漏洞百出，港共被迫配合搬龍門，e.g.基本法22條、內會主席、國安法。<br />\n<br />\n故此，我地應避免與已接近無限擴大了的職權硬碰硬，反而本土戰線應利用其核核突突之處作加速主義，使外資跳船，不夠深紅嘅自私狗陷入砍難，最後令到香港可以帶住中共一齊攬炒。表態嘅遊行示威已經非常多，國際間輿論已十分偏向我地。個人認為已經冇咩必要不斷出去肉身食子彈，本地抗爭轉型係呢刻十分必要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要我們還活著，就有很多事是可以去期待的。革命好漫長，有手足要坐以十年計嘅監，我地就要係出面堅持做十年計嘅抗爭。盲目嘅抗爭及情緒主導難以令抗爭持續，波蘭嘅手段極之具參考價值。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">是時候轉守為攻，不再作悲情文宣，應把抗爭轉化成生活的一部分，宣傳光復後的美好將來，主力探討獨立條件及實際操作。同時戰線地下化，繼續及增強國際遊說及被捕者支援，為真正煲底之日作好準備。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2a1aJAw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2a1aJAw.jpg&h=34511c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\nNever Forget, Never Forgive.<br />\n<br />\n香港人，建國。</div></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"全民貼美國國旗🇺🇸已經可以"},{"pid":"31cdea6c7952157d78f030a43de498e9be380404","tid":2041033,"uid":345255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"大叫支那狗 完。"},{"pid":"ee2c11de71c05aa5354da31638e9ce5e862b02e2","tid":2041033,"uid":307999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:19:14.000Z","msg":"baby xi balloon?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7Z0pVW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7Z0pVW.jpg&h=279ab4d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aba00df796bbfe6c014ba1d24c0caab6492fb1e","tid":2041033,"uid":336922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e51a26eda1afb1c30fa38edde3679b99930fe156","tid":2041033,"uid":236538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/2cdbf5de-10c7-11ea-bbc7-005056a99247/w:900/p:16x9/capturexietsesamantes.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F2cdbf5de-10c7-11ea-bbc7-005056a99247%2Fw%3A900%2Fp%3A16x9%2Fcapturexietsesamantes.png&h=072bedbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"愛情故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7296b25b375440c06a3294bb586a367d32646d4b","tid":2041033,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e1e6e3fcb63dc616b9a6329f31394861b02d36","tid":2041033,"uid":184599,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"09d8c841337688ea162412468ddf962340ee9ca5","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TL;DR 創意抗爭更能吸引外媒目光，使參與抗爭門檻更低，幽默情節在社會中更能成為話題。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n國安法將臨，雖然國際間好消息不絕，但離中共倒台仍確實有一段距離。經過1年的精神繃緊，不少和理非及淺黃已拒絕接收抗爭消息或出席任何集會遊行。5.27等目標不明確的集會、黃店/kol互咬、捉鬼隊、送頭論等亦使眾手足不斷內鬥、互罵、消耗抗爭能量，使情勢不容樂觀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，希望大家要面對現實，我地依家追求嘅唔再係五大訴求咁簡單，係民族自治、係脫離中共管治、係港獨、係推翻中共政權。 At least, 對家係咁諗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6CUqOG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6CUqOG.jpg&h=12bf7bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地眼前嘅敵人已經不再是擅長分化淺黃、可以遊花園遊到去對面海等較高章政治手段嘅港共政權，或者周身屎嘅販冰兵，而係不惜搲爛塊面都要作戰狼外交、有前冇後嘅中共團隊。縱然其資源及權力都較港共多及大，但手段漏洞百出，港共被迫配合搬龍門，e.g.基本法22條、內會主席、國安法。<br />\n<br />\n故此，我地應避免與已接近無限擴大了的職權硬碰硬，反而本土戰線應利用其核核突突之處作加速主義，使外資跳船，不夠深紅嘅自私狗陷入砍難，最後令到香港可以帶住中共一齊攬炒。表態嘅遊行示威已經非常多，國際間輿論已十分偏向我地。個人認為已經冇咩必要不斷出去肉身食子彈，本地抗爭轉型係呢刻十分必要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要我們還活著，就有很多事是可以去期待的。革命好漫長，有手足要坐以十年計嘅監，我地就要係出面堅持做十年計嘅抗爭。盲目嘅抗爭及情緒主導難以令抗爭持續，波蘭嘅手段極之具參考價值。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">是時候轉守為攻，不再作悲情文宣，應把抗爭轉化成生活的一部分，宣傳光復後的美好將來，主力探討獨立條件及實際操作。同時戰線地下化，繼續及增強國際遊說及被捕者支援，為真正煲底之日作好準備。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2a1aJAw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2a1aJAw.jpg&h=34511c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\nNever Forget, Never Forgive.<br />\n<br />\n香港人，建國。</div></span></strong>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:34:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">玩快閃即聚即散</span></span></strong><br />\n唱國歌又得，開遮又得，撒黃黑旗又得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">騎劫任何大型活動</span></span></span></strong></span><br />\n一有大型活動即做手勢或口號<br />\n演唱會完場/中場就叫口號<br />\n有直播/傳媒嘅活動就做burn with us手勢<br />\n總之只要有中共一日，革命之火永不熄滅"},{"pid":"d66b781510a7542f3c4062be2e8a70292977bc8d","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c589ac410b438fd625ff914e16efb0f0365ecfc8","tid":2041033,"uid":306621,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c34983377e742761f90739d7f890c81e46b60f4d","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"like":90,"dislike":3,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"閱讀前提<br />\n1, 香港人可以將抗爭融入生活 e.g.黃色經濟圈。<br />\n2, 香港獨立逐漸成為主流，留戀街頭抗爭意義及目的不大。<br />\n3, 狗隻已完全掌握過去1年嘅所有抗爭模式 e.g. 5.27港九新界佈陣。<br />\n4, 勇武抗爭到達樽頸位，面對水炮車、震撼彈等理大戰時所用武器已經無計可施，同時難以在本地升級 e.g. 炸藥、槍、軍隊。<br />\n5, 裝修對經濟打擊喺旅遊業復甦前不大，影響亦遠不及一次武漢肺炎。<br />\n6, 唔駛諗咩大罷工同全民勇武。講咗成年喇，死心啦。手足擋子彈擋到變蜂巢都唔會罷工。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:24:18.000Z","msg":"即係叫人咩都唔好做, 食黃店, 幻想自己抗爭咗, 然後再過一代人,<br />\n香港人變成小粉紅, <br />\n<br />\n我既理解有冇錯?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"我就係叫緊大家一齊諗新嘅抗爭模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4e36fd76778c2e9cd26ade4b7dae3c29401981","tid":2041033,"uid":263067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7571f227efa909eb05ff3cdfb646f23e4854e0bf","tid":2041033,"uid":161504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:39:02.000Z","msg":"Push!!!"},{"pid":"60813dd7c5f7dd2f2b950e5b96b39e78da7f3a3e","tid":2041033,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"全面著黑衫好似已經好our<br />\n震d低成本 又表達到民意嘅方法<br />\n比國際社會見到 香港人唔會放棄爭取自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0141f7dd31012edaac739bc970b30194f17e3c","tid":2041033,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84e1e6e3fcb63dc616b9a6329f31394861b02d36","tid":2041033,"uid":184599,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"09d8c841337688ea162412468ddf962340ee9ca5","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TL;DR 創意抗爭更能吸引外媒目光，使參與抗爭門檻更低，幽默情節在社會中更能成為話題。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n國安法將臨，雖然國際間好消息不絕，但離中共倒台仍確實有一段距離。經過1年的精神繃緊，不少和理非及淺黃已拒絕接收抗爭消息或出席任何集會遊行。5.27等目標不明確的集會、黃店/kol互咬、捉鬼隊、送頭論等亦使眾手足不斷內鬥、互罵、消耗抗爭能量，使情勢不容樂觀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，希望大家要面對現實，我地依家追求嘅唔再係五大訴求咁簡單，係民族自治、係脫離中共管治、係港獨、係推翻中共政權。 At least, 對家係咁諗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6CUqOG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6CUqOG.jpg&h=12bf7bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地眼前嘅敵人已經不再是擅長分化淺黃、可以遊花園遊到去對面海等較高章政治手段嘅港共政權，或者周身屎嘅販冰兵，而係不惜搲爛塊面都要作戰狼外交、有前冇後嘅中共團隊。縱然其資源及權力都較港共多及大，但手段漏洞百出，港共被迫配合搬龍門，e.g.基本法22條、內會主席、國安法。<br />\n<br />\n故此，我地應避免與已接近無限擴大了的職權硬碰硬，反而本土戰線應利用其核核突突之處作加速主義，使外資跳船，不夠深紅嘅自私狗陷入砍難，最後令到香港可以帶住中共一齊攬炒。表態嘅遊行示威已經非常多，國際間輿論已十分偏向我地。個人認為已經冇咩必要不斷出去肉身食子彈，本地抗爭轉型係呢刻十分必要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要我們還活著，就有很多事是可以去期待的。革命好漫長，有手足要坐以十年計嘅監，我地就要係出面堅持做十年計嘅抗爭。盲目嘅抗爭及情緒主導難以令抗爭持續，波蘭嘅手段極之具參考價值。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">是時候轉守為攻，不再作悲情文宣，應把抗爭轉化成生活的一部分，宣傳光復後的美好將來，主力探討獨立條件及實際操作。同時戰線地下化，繼續及增強國際遊說及被捕者支援，為真正煲底之日作好準備。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2a1aJAw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2a1aJAw.jpg&h=34511c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\nNever Forget, Never Forgive.<br />\n<br />\n香港人，建國。</div></span></strong>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:34:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">玩快閃即聚即散</span></span></strong><br />\n唱國歌又得，開遮又得，撒黃黑旗又得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">騎劫任何大型活動</span></span></span></strong></span><br />\n一有大型活動即做手勢或口號<br />\n演唱會完場/中場就叫口號<br />\n有直播/傳媒嘅活動就做burn with us手勢<br />\n總之只要有中共一日，革命之火永不熄滅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:40:04.000Z","msg":"好似幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fa3f498684883aefe7356de36772a0c5a56a0f","tid":2041033,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"多謝蔡英文大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cacf81e12de60db09ce2eeb501f1bdf5bae9648","tid":2041033,"uid":140309,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b0fe0b1109ce0b7b271d1b261040cdd529ce3f4f","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"l