01YyMGEZOa9B33KGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=cc237c0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9m556StrkwQ</a>"},{"pid":"4f3329005af16c13b5ee3cb0b39d3926ae02a6cd","tid":2041033,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:50:30.000Z","msg":"紅底黃字<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">支持国安取代港警 解決黑暴問題</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11845995fdb37275be76ca1893a19da38df3813b","tid":2041033,"uid":209603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09d8c841337688ea162412468ddf962340ee9ca5","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TL;DR 創意抗爭更能吸引外媒目光，使參與抗爭門檻更低，幽默情節在社會中更能成為話題。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n國安法將臨，雖然國際間好消息不絕，但離中共倒台仍確實有一段距離。經過1年的精神繃緊，不少和理非及淺黃已拒絕接收抗爭消息或出席任何集會遊行。5.27等目標不明確的集會、黃店/kol互咬、捉鬼隊、送頭論等亦使眾手足不斷內鬥、互罵、消耗抗爭能量，使情勢不容樂觀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，希望大家要面對現實，我地依家追求嘅唔再係五大訴求咁簡單，係民族自治、係脫離中共管治、係港獨、係推翻中共政權。 At least, 對家係咁諗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6CUqOG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6CUqOG.jpg&h=12bf7bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地眼前嘅敵人已經不再是擅長分化淺黃、可以遊花園遊到去對面海等較高章政治手段嘅港共政權，或者周身屎嘅販冰兵，而係不惜搲爛塊面都要作戰狼外交、有前冇後嘅中共團隊。縱然其資源及權力都較港共多及大，但手段漏洞百出，港共被迫配合搬龍門，e.g.基本法22條、內會主席、國安法。<br />\n<br />\n故此，我地應避免與已接近無限擴大了的職權硬碰硬，反而本土戰線應利用其核核突突之處作加速主義，使外資跳船，不夠深紅嘅自私狗陷入砍難，最後令到香港可以帶住中共一齊攬炒。表態嘅遊行示威已經非常多，國際間輿論已十分偏向我地。個人認為已經冇咩必要不斷出去肉身食子彈，本地抗爭轉型係呢刻十分必要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要我們還活著，就有很多事是可以去期待的。革命好漫長，有手足要坐以十年計嘅監，我地就要係出面堅持做十年計嘅抗爭。盲目嘅抗爭及情緒主導難以令抗爭持續，波蘭嘅手段極之具參考價值。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">是時候轉守為攻，不再作悲情文宣，應把抗爭轉化成生活的一部分，宣傳光復後的美好將來，主力探討獨立條件及實際操作。同時戰線地下化，繼續及增強國際遊說及被捕者支援，為真正煲底之日作好準備。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2a1aJAw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2a1aJAw.jpg&h=34511c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\nNever Forget, Never Forgive.<br />\n<br />\n香港人，建國。</div></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62OTFJk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62OTFJk.png&h=c31b2f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mArU9BG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmArU9BG.png&h=f55d2c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩步share文宣大法！㩒兩個制都唔肯㩒你仲係咪香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入去個website揀張圖 㩒share去whatsapp 就可以send哂俾親戚朋友同各大群組<br />\n都可以share上Facebook同twitter！<br />\n非常清晰簡潔嘅介面俾你下載落黎擺ig<br />\n<br />\n全民文宣呀！！！ <br />\n<a href=\"https://swallowlife.org/lennon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fswallowlife.org%2Flennon&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33KGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=e10c0181\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://swallowlife.org/lennon</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主幫手置頂得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ed142b3c1599c9228505666ad29f43a49d7561","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:55:54.000Z","msg":"中共：好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9594ed418ec55d6ae3f6722684e17ec4ca41f809","tid":2041033,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c905e2a837e3efd2dcc0c2f65adfcafb205f77f","tid":2041033,"uid":2529,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score